pageTitle: Jam Defender - Yu-Gi-Oh! - It's time to Duel!
title: European English
textBeforeTable: English—Worldwide TCG sets Yu-Gi-Oh! only When your opponent targets a monster on your side of the field for an attack and you control a face-up "Revival Jam", switch the target to "Revival Jam". If your opponent activates a card effect that inflicts effect damage you can destroy 1 "Revival Jam" you control to negate the card's activation and destroy it. If you would take Battle Damage, you can destroy 1 "Revival Jam" you control to reduce the Battle Damage to 0. English anime
